## [Pricing]

### Headline
Less than one day's guide fee.

$500 to build. $35 a month.

That covers hosting, SSL, DNS, unlimited content updates, and direct access to the developer who built your site. No contracts. Month to month.

One extra booking per season pays for your website for the entire year.

### Add-ons
Stripe deposit collection: +$250 build, no additional monthly.
Seasonal availability calendar: +$250 build, no additional monthly.

---

## [What You Don't Get]

No Airbnb-style commissions. No FishingBooker taking 20% of every trip. No WordPress plugin nightmares. No call center — you deal with the developer directly, and the developer deals with your site.

