## Page Notes

- Hero photo: full-width Montana landscape (river/mountain, golden hour). Dark overlay with light text.
- The Problem section: no photo needed, just clean text on sand background.
- Features section: could use trip card mockup screenshots or availability calendar screenshot from the demo.
- Pricing section: dark timber background with cream text. Keep it simple — the math does the work.
- Email signup: forest green button, prominent placement. This is the primary conversion goal.
- Total word count target: ~400-500 words visible on page. Short. Every sentence earns its place.
